Package de.fhtw.xgl.interpreter

Contains basic interfaces for the interaction between the XGL-GUI and the application logic.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
CallbackHandler Defines the connection with the application logic.
Interpreter The Interpreter is the core-class of the XML-gui.
Widget Basic GUI-element.
 

Exception Summary
XglInterpreterException Indicates that an Exception appeared during the parsing of the XML-structure.
